---
import LayoutPage from "../../layouts/LayoutPage.astro";
import { getLangFromUrl } from "../../i18n/utils";
import { getHomePath } from "../../i18n/paths";

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const homeHref = getHomePath(lang);

const lastUpdated = "April 12, 2025";
---

<LayoutPage
  title="Privacy Policy | Sonmyd — Miguel Zuluaga"
  description="Privacy policy and personal data processing at Sonmyd, in accordance with Colombian Law 1581 of 2012 and GDPR."
>
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div class="u-container content">
      <a href={homeHref} class="back-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M17 10a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75H5.612l4.158 3.96a.75.75 0 1 1-1.04 1.08l-5.5-5.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.08l5.5-5.25a.75.75 0 1 1 1.04 1.08L5.612 9.25H16.25A.75.75 0 0 1 17 10Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        {lang === "en" ? "Back to home" : "Volver al inicio"}
      </a>

      <h1 class="u-heading page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="meta u-text">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose u-text">
        <p>
          At <strong>Sonmyd</strong> (operated by Miguel Zuluaga) we are committed to protecting your privacy and
          processing your personal data in accordance with <strong>Colombian Law 1581 of 2012</strong> and
          <strong>Decree 1377 of 2013</strong>, and where applicable, the European Union's General Data Protection
          Regulation (GDPR).
        </p>
        <p>
          By using our website <a href="https://sonmyd.co">sonmyd.co</a> or contacting us, you accept
          the practices described in this policy.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Name:</strong> Miguel Zuluaga<br />
          <strong>Brand:</strong> Sonmyd<br />
          <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://sonmyd.co">sonmyd.co</a><br />
          <strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/573106041144" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>
        </p>

        <h2>2. Data we collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following personal data when you voluntarily provide it:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Full name</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Phone number / WhatsApp</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Plan of interest</strong> (information about the service you're interested in)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Additionally, we automatically collect technical data such as IP address, browser type,
          pages visited and time spent, through third-party analytics tools.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Processing purposes</h2>
        <p>We use your data to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact you to confirm bookings and provide the requested service.</li>
          <li>Send you relevant information about AI mentorship services.</li>
          <li>Improve the website experience and personalize content.</li>
          <li>Analyze traffic and site performance via Google Analytics / Google Tag Manager.</li>
          <li>Prevent fraudulent activity (honeypot and rate limiting on forms).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Legal basis</h2>
        <p>Data processing is carried out based on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Your explicit consent</strong> when submitting the contact form or contacting us directly.</li>
          <li><strong>Performance of the service contract</strong> you have requested.</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> in improving and protecting the website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Data storage</h2>
        <p>
          Contact form data is securely stored in <strong>Supabase</strong>,
          a database platform hosted on SOC 2 certified servers. Only the Provider has access to this data.
        </p>
        <p>
          We retain your data as long as an active business relationship exists or as long as necessary
          for the stated purposes. You can request deletion at any time.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Cookies and tracking technologies</h2>
        <p>
          We use <strong>Google Tag Manager</strong> and <strong>Google Analytics</strong> to collect
          anonymous statistical usage data about site visits. These tools may use first-party and third-party cookies.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can manage your cookie preferences from your browser settings. Note that disabling certain cookies
          may affect site functionality.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Third-party sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell or transfer your personal data to third parties for commercial purposes. Data may be
          processed by the following trusted service providers, under strict confidentiality obligations:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — form data storage.</li>
          <li><strong>Google (Analytics / Tag Manager)</strong> — web traffic analysis.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. International transfers</h2>
        <p>
          Some listed providers operate outside Colombia. In such cases, we ensure that adequate protection
          guarantees are in place in accordance with current regulations.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          Under Law 1581 of 2012 and, where applicable, the GDPR, you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li><strong>Rectify</strong> incorrect or outdated data.</li>
          <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data when no longer necessary for the stated purposes.</li>
          <li><strong>Object</strong> to the processing of your data for marketing purposes.</li>
          <li><strong>Revoke</strong> your consent at any time, without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing.</li>
          <li><strong>Lodge a complaint</strong> with the Colombian Superintendency of Industry and Commerce (SIC)
            or your national data protection authority.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, contact us via
          <a href="https://wa.me/573106041144" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>.
          We will respond within a maximum of 15 business days.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized
          access, loss or alteration. However, no internet transmission is completely secure; data is used
          under your responsibility when shared with us.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Minors</h2>
        <p>
          Our services are intended for people over 18 years of age. We do not intentionally collect
          data from minors. If we detect that a minor has provided us data without parental consent,
          we will delete it immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>12. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy at any time. Changes will be published on this page with the
          new update date. We recommend reviewing it periodically.
        </p>

        <h2>13. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any inquiries, questions or requests related to this privacy policy, contact us via
          <a href="https://wa.me/573106041144" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutPage>

<style>
  .page-wrap {
    padding: 9rem 0 8rem;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4em;
    color: rgba(240, 240, 250, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;

    svg { width: 1em; height: 1em; }
    &:hover { color: rgba(240, 240, 250, 0.9); }
  }

  .content { max-width: 48rem; }

  .page-title {
    --fs: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;

    @media (--mq-phone) { --fs: 2.2rem; }
  }

  .meta {
    --fs: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-alt);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .prose {
    --fs: var(--font-size-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(240, 240, 250, 0.8);

    p { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

    h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-roboto-slab);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgb(var(--rgb-text));
      margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(50, 170, 255, 0.15);
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;

      li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    }

    strong { color: rgb(var(--rgb-text)); font-weight: 600; }

    a {
      color: rgb(var(--rgb-brand-2));
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-color: rgba(50, 170, 255, 0.4);
      transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s;

      &:hover { text-decoration-color: rgba(50, 170, 255, 1); }
    }
  }
</style>
